cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on natural language processing (NLP) and contextualized word representations, which are key topics in this field. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper deals with automatic speech recognition (ASR) and spoken language understanding. 
- cs.SI (Signal Processing) is another possible category as the paper involves processing and analyzing audio signals. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a novel fine-tuning method for pre-trained language models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that could also apply, as the paper involves using machine learning techniques to improve NLP performance on ASR transcripts.
